FT  30 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Blockleys
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Blockleys, the Shropshire-based brick and pavior manufacturer, reported a 36
per cent decline in pre-tax profits, from Pounds 410,000 to Pounds 261,000,
for the six months to end-June.
The outcome was struck on turnover down by Pounds 391,000 to Pounds 4.75m
